WEBVTT

00:00.300 --> 00:02.601
Previously on <i>Royal Pains...</i>
<i>Dmitry is back.</i>

00:02.617 --> 00:03.866
Do you really think
he had something to do

00:03.868 --> 00:05.318
- with Boris's death?
- I don't know.

00:05.320 --> 00:06.653
But I'm gonna find out.

00:06.655 --> 00:08.270
I think I figured out Dmitry's motive.

00:08.272 --> 00:10.540
Boris and Dmitry were brothers.

00:10.542 --> 00:12.659
His name is Milos. He's Boris's cousin.

00:12.661 --> 00:14.460
He seems really upset
about Boris's death.

00:14.462 --> 00:15.778
So when are you meeting up with him?

00:15.780 --> 00:16.996
He lives in Budapest.

00:16.998 --> 00:20.299
Your HCG levels have plateaued.

00:20.301 --> 00:22.284
This pregnancy may not be viable.

00:22.286 --> 00:23.920
So we met with Shelby.
She offered to have us

00:23.922 --> 00:25.838
take a look at their hospital
in Savannah.

00:25.840 --> 00:27.256
I'll go.

00:27.258 --> 00:28.307
Would you want to go along?

00:28.309 --> 00:30.643
Georgia. I'm willing to travel.

00:30.645 --> 00:32.061
Great, it's this weekend.

00:32.063 --> 00:33.295
What about you?

00:33.297 --> 00:35.131
Oh, I'm not going. Just Divya.

00:35.133 --> 00:36.566
And now, you.

00:36.568 --> 00:38.151
This is a cease and desist order.

00:38.153 --> 00:39.769
The use of the home professional office

00:39.771 --> 00:41.971
shall be prohibited.

00:41.973 --> 00:44.974
[Upbeat music]

00:44.976 --> 00:45.476
d

00:46.365 --> 00:50.315
www.NapiProjekt.pl - nowa jakoœæ napisów.
